doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content="Nat Carey's personal website. Nat is a musician, comedian, software engineer and more.")
        meta(name='author', content='Nat Carey')

        title Nat Carey (she/her)

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Catamaran:100,200,300,400,500,600,700,800,900' rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,100i,300,300i,400,400i,700,700i,900,900i' rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.navbar-custom.fixed-top
            .container.px-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') Nat Carey

        // Header
        header.masthead.text-center.text-white
            .masthead-content
                .container.px-5
                    h1.masthead-heading.mb-0 Nat Carey (she/her)
                    h2.masthead-subheading.mb-0 Musician, Comedian, Software Engineer
            .bg-circle-1.bg-circle
            .bg-circle-2.bg-circle
            .bg-circle-3.bg-circle
            .bg-circle-4.bg-circle

        // Content section 1
        section#scroll
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/01.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Hi, I'm Nat
                            p
                                | I'm Nat, I have too many hobbies.  I'll share some of them here but there are always more.

        // Content section 2
        section
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/02.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Comedy
                            p
                                | I perform queer, feminist comedy.  I've heard many many (male) commedians say "You can't joke about anything anymore".
                                | I joke about all sorts of things - sexuality, gender pay gap, parenting, sexuality.
                                | I call on my own experiences with each of these things and try to make some oignant points alongside/through the jokes.

        // Content section 3
        section
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-2
                        .p-5
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='assets/img/03.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-1
                        .p-5
                            h2.display-4 Music
                            p
                                | I've been playing music since I was 10, it's been so important to me for much of this time.
                                | I play drums, guitar, bass, I dabble on keys and vocals.  Mostly at the moment I'm producing.
                                | I have produced one album and I'm working on more.

        // Footer
        footer.py-5.bg-black
            .container.px-5
                p.m-0.text-center.text-white.small Copyright &copy; Nat Carey 2022

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
